{"tid":697252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel電影部: 將會更重用女性導演和演員","createTime":"2018-06-10T23:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T07:26:50.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3ceec4d8f5ed986c9db66d6b871d923bbbcdaf23","tid":697252,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:37:26.000Z","msg":"Marvel電影部門的主席Kevin Feige: 《黑豹》是最佳的自家製作, 未來會更重用女性演員和導演<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.indiewire.com/2018/06/kevin-feige-secrets-marvel-universe-produced-by-conference-1201973150/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2018%2F06%2Fkevin-feige-secrets-marvel-universe-produced-by-conference-1201973150%2F&d=l9VKxDsGp6iGW%2FHX6EPx8DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f76caa4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.indiewire.com/2018/06/kevin-feige-secrets-marvel-universe-produced-by-conference-1201973150/</a><br />\n<br />\nKevin Feige on the Future of Marvel: More Women, More Diversity, and More Sequels<br />\n<br />\nThe Marvel wizard who pulls the strings at the MCU came out from behind the curtain at the Produced By Conference 2018.<br />\n<br />\nAnne Thompson<br />\n7 hours ago<br />\n<br />\nWith more than $16 billion in global box office, how does Marvel do it? It boils down to Kevin Feige, sole producer of 19 Marvel movies since &ldquo;Iron Man&rdquo; in 2008, all of which opened at number one. Marvel&rsquo;s master is a Boston-born, New Jersey-raised movie nerd who collected ticket stubs, sat through &ldquo;Star Wars: The Phantom Menace&rdquo; 13 times and was rejected by USC film school four or five times before being accepted.<br />\n..........<br />\nLean into diversity<br />\n<br />\n<strong>&ldquo;Black Panther&rdquo; was a transformative experience, said Feige. When he saw the final movie, he turned to writer-director Ryan Coogler and said, &ldquo;That&rsquo;s the best movie we&rsquo;ve ever made.&rdquo; At the junket he told the director, &ldquo;You&rsquo;ve made us a better studio.&rdquo;</strong> Coogler&rsquo;s suggestions for production and costume designers and cinematographer were all better than the ones Marvel had in mind, added Feige.<br />\n<br />\nFeige&rsquo;s goal for that movie: &ldquo;It had to succeed to disprove the myth that black movies don&rsquo;t perform around the world.&rdquo; He continued, &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t want to be in a room where everyone looks like you. It&rsquo;s detrimental to the project you are working on.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Add women before and behind the camera</strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Ant-Man and The Wasp&rdquo; has just finished in time for its July 6 release. It&rsquo;s the first Marvel movie with a co-title female hero, Evangeline Lily&rsquo;s Wasp, ahead of Brie Larson as &ldquo;Captain Marvel,&rdquo; which is the first movie with a woman director &mdash; Anna Boden co-directs her with husband Ryan Fleck &mdash; with writing credits going to six women and Fleck. &ldquo;No matter how liberal you think you are,&rdquo; said Feige, &ldquo;unconscious bias is a real thing.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The agencies are stepping up, he said, sending Marvel more women than men for future assignments. &ldquo;A heck of a lot&rdquo; of their upcoming movies will be directed by women, he promised.</strong><br />\n<br />\nRein in costs<br />\n<br />\nThe movies will cost more because the above-the-line costs keep going up, said Feige. &ldquo;Over the years, the actors deserve to get paid.&rdquo; But he insists the below-the-line stays much the same. &ldquo;Money won&rsquo;t solve a creative problem,&rdquo; he said.<br />\nAdd comedy<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;My favorite movies have comic moments,&rdquo; he said. From the start with &ldquo;Iron Man,&rdquo; Jon Favreau took the characters seriously but allowed them to get into funny situations. &ldquo;That worked quite well and was a lesson for us,&rdquo; said Feige. &ldquo;If you get the audience laughing with you, have a better chance of getting other emotions along the way.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"39db0f935afd2b289f0748aa022baf244ad693a2","tid":697252,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"睇下係咪會票房大跌吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24843710095d224ccc86b6d0f062f5ca64664432","tid":697252,"uid":33481,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"39db0f935afd2b289f0748aa022baf244ad693a2","tid":697252,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"睇下係咪會票房大跌吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:58:40.000Z","msg":"過埋出年無限之戰仲有撚人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a045539437d6d333a3dab45b707d4f42582233","tid":697252,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"加黑鬼就變成最佳？"},{"pid":"5ad5a046375cf6497e59cbfc8eac752109bf498c","tid":697252,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"59a045539437d6d333a3dab45b707d4f42582233","tid":697252,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"加黑鬼就變成最佳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:19:18.000Z","msg":"《黑豹》的確拍得好好。"},{"pid":"b8c2e408e3e4884677420300fdb7d4c05c92469f","tid":697252,"uid":4917,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"5ad5a046375cf6497e59cbfc8eac752109bf498c","tid":697252,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"59a045539437d6d333a3dab45b707d4f42582233","tid":697252,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"加黑鬼就變成最佳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:19:18.000Z","msg":"《黑豹》的確拍得好好。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"一般水準"},{"pid":"6ac6219bab58dbe1e1e7991b1739703d651e2a7d","tid":697252,"uid":108467,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8c2e